snippet.title: Pennine ishtayo? | 4k | Short film | full movie | Sajin | Gopika anil | Achu sugandh
snippet.description:
Pennine Ishtayo - A Musical Short Film | Official Release
"Pennine Ishtayo" is a captivating Malayalam musical short film that explores the deep emotions of love, human connection, and the power of music. Directed by Achu Sugandh and produced by Nithin Thaivalappil under Filmika Cinemas, this film features powerful performances by Sajin Shiva, Gopika Anil, and an ensemble cast of talented actors. With stunning visuals by Rejin Santo and soul-stirring music composed by Bonny Louis, this film is sure to resonate with viewers of all ages.

From the mesmerizing vocals by Sadhika K R, Neethusha A C, Arjun, Nithin K Shiva, and Bonny Louis, to the skillful dance choreography by Surya R K, Pennine Ishtayi is a complete sensory experience that beautifully blends narrative and music.

Key Credits:

Written & Directed by: Achu Sugandh
Produced by: Nithin Thaivalappil, Filmika Cinemas
Cinematography (DoP): Rejin Santo
Music Director: Bonny Louis
Editor: Anandhu S Vijay
Sound Engineer: Aashif Ali
Colorist: Ebin Philip
Mix & Master: Arjun B Nair

Featuring:

Sajin Shiva
Gopika Anil
Vijaya Sadan
James Parackkal
Rahul
Sathwik
Milan Sandra

Juman

en.title: Pennine ishtayo? | 4k | Short film | full movie | Sajin | Gopika anil | Achu sugandh
en.description:
Pennine Ishtayo - A Musical Short Film | Official Release
"Pennine Ishtayo" is a captivating Malayalam musical short film that explores the deep emotions of love, human connection, and the power of music. Directed by Achu Sugandh and produced by Nithin Thaivalappil under Filmika Cinemas, this film features powerful performances by Sajin Shiva, Gopika Anil, and an ensemble cast of talented actors. With stunning visuals by Rejin Santo and soul-stirring music composed by Bonny Louis, this film is sure to resonate with viewers of all ages.

From the mesmerizing vocals by Sadhika K R, Neethusha A C, Arjun, Nithin K Shiva, and Bonny Louis, to the skillful dance choreography by Surya R K, Pennine Ishtayi is a complete sensory experience that beautifully blends narrative and music.

snippet.title: Karnataka bypoll election result 2024: Congress wins all three seats
snippet.description:
The ruling Congress in Karnataka is jubilant after winning Legislative Assembly bypolls in all three constituencies of Channapatna, Shiggaon and Sandur

All three constituencies witnessed a direct fight between the Congress and Opposition BJP-JD(S) alliance. While the Congress wrested Channapatna and Shiggaon seats from the JD(S) and the BJP, respectively, it retained the Sandur seat.

With these results, the Congress tally in the Karnataka Assembly went up to 137.

For live updates on Maharashtra Assembly elections, click here: https://www.thehindu.com/elections/maharashtra-assembly/maharashtra-assembly-election-results-live-updates-mahayuti-maha-vikas-aghadi-shiv-sena-november-23-2024/article68897964.ece

snippet.title: Dhiktana Dhiktana - The Hustle Flip l Mad Trip  | MTV Hustle 4
snippet.description:
"This song is a reimagined version of the classic Bollywood track 'Dhiktana Dhiktana', transformed into a melancholic reflection on loneliness and disillusionment. By flipping the upbeat original into a somber tone, the song conveys the harsh reality that no one in this world truly belongs to you. It redefines the familiar melody to evoke a sense of sadness and introspection, making it a poignant commentary on isolation and unfulfilled connections.

Song Credits

Track Name: Dhiktana Dhiktana - The Hustle Flip
Written & Performed By: @MadTrip05 
Music Producer: Aditya Pushkarna
Primary Artist: @MadTrip05 
Track Name: Dhiktana Dhiktana - The Hustle Flip
Singer/Performed By/Cast: @MadTrip05 
Lyricist/Written By: @MadTrip05 
Music Produced By: Aditya Pushkarna
Co-Composer: Aditya Pushkarna
Music Label: Saregama
Genre: Hip Hop
Sub-Genre: Rap
Language:Hindi
Country of Origin/Source: India

üëâ Subscribe to KaanPhod : https://www.youtube.com/@KaanPhodMusic 
üëâ Like us on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/kaanphod 
üëâ Follow us on X: https://x.com/kaanphodmusic?s=11 
üëâ Follow us on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/kaanphodmusic/ 


Lyrics

Mad Trip@MadTrip05 

Kaisa hai tu kaise hain sab 
Poochhe khairiyat par dekhe haisiyat sab
pata chala sirf paison se rishte Hain
toh ab mere sirf paison se rishte hain

Haan maine jeet dekhi 
Haan maine  haar dekhi
Tedha bann ke chalna padta
Warna neki maar degi

Sadkon pe maar dekhi
Apno mein khaar dekhi
Qatl-e-aam ki khabrein Aksar 
qabrein toh aam dekhi

Dekhi saanp Seedhi
Baatein likhun saaf seedhi
Kisi ko bhi Sunn-ni nahi hai
Yahan pe meri aap beeti

Rishton mein rajneeti
Kisse bas jaydaad ke hisse na khaak mili
kishton mein haar mili

Dekhi Kitni shakal gayi pal mein Badal
mere Seene mein kyun hoti Har pal hulchul

Har pal chanchal mann karey bhag-dadd
Ab dil mera khaali Ghar lage khandar

Ghooma nahi main duniya  jahaanon mein kabhi 
Kyun ki pehle se hi maine dekh liya sab shayad
Bura waqt bhi dikha ke jaayega ek Jaadu 
Tu Khaali 10 tak ginn ho jayenge sab gayab

Ae khuda mujhe kya hua
Kyun lagta yeh begaana
Tu bataa main hoon kahan
Manzil ki raah dikhlana

Dhiktana dhiktana dhiktana
Yahan apno mein apna koi dikhta na
Dhiktana tiktana dhiktana
Saala sacchi mein saccha koi rishta na

Dhiktana dhiktana dhiktana
Yahan apno mein apna koi dikhta na
Dhiktana tiktana dhiktana
Saala sacchi mein saccha koi rishta na

Dhiktana tiktana dhiktana
Dhik dhiktana dhiktana dhiktana

Dhiktana dhiktana dhiktana
Dhik dhiktana dhiktana dhiktana

Aansu toh roz aaye par koi na ponchh paaye 
Bolun dil ki baatein par dil tak nahi yeh pahunch paaye
Dhokhe toh bahut khaaye woh toh roz ka hai 
Saare apna soche tu apno ka sochta hai kyun

doon main ghar walon ko dosh jo sochte mera roz
Afsos main unpe bojh main Kosta khud ko bahut
Jailon se bhi zyaada logon ke mann mein hai chor 
woh dekhe kab dheela ho naada 
kab kheenche langot

Jaana kahan soojhta bhi nahi
Ho Bhookhe paet nange paanv 
toh koi thookta bhi nahi
sawaal ka jawaab dene se baney crorepati
Lekin hum jaison ko yahan koi poochhta hi nahi

Bina taane khaaye  milti hain taaliyaan bhi na
Milti kaamyabi toh yeh dekhe khaamiyan bhi na

Kaafi ghalatiyan bhi Kari 
ghalati se seekha bhi main
Yeh duniya ek kitaab toh baatein kitaabi yeh
Chunautiyaan hain log hai kya ismein koi shaq
Roz bolun bhagwan se Enough is enough

Kaash Miley hote gham kam re
Humein bhi koi miley hote humdum re
Ghutt-te hain andar hi andar se
Ab Chubhte hain mujh ko yeh bandh kamre

Main So paaun kabhi chain se
Aise bhi din dikhlana 
Kho jaaunga bheed mein
Tu haath thaam lega na

Dhiktana tiktana dhiktana
Yahan apno mein apna koi dikhta na
Dhiktana tiktana  dhiktana
Saala sacchi mein saccha koi rishta na

Dhiktana tiktana dhiktana
Yahan apno mein apna koi dikhta na
Dhiktana tiktana dhiktana
Saala sacchi mein saccha koi rishta na

Apno ko dekha apno se ladte toh apna hai kaun aaya ek sawaal
Gairon ko dekha maine zakhmon ko bharte toh apna hai kaun phir aaya ek sawaal

This Video shows all the crazy fun that happens in Big Fat Indian weddings. Indias and wedding season madness . Brides going on crazy diets to loose weight before Marriage , the morning after wedding and playing shadi rasam games with new bhahi and bhaiya like kagna games , Pre Bridal functions like mata ki choki , cocktail , sanjeet , roka , sagai , god tika , struggles of love marriage , cousins and best friends planning bachelorette for bride of the group , haldi ceremony and bhai behen getting emotional , Relatives giving advices about marriage. All the money , gifts , wedding preps , indian food , gol gappe , tikki , chart items , Paneer Tikka ,  spicy food , indian sweets , shaadi lehenga , bride makeup , wedding shopping , crazy dancing on wedding songs . Indian aunties taking lime light . Mehendi functions getting henna done and celebrating with family , friends , cousins . Ldki Wale vs ladke Wale , wedding photographers , pharo time and shadi wali coffee and crying on bidai , attending Big Fat Indian weddings like Kohli Tents , Flying Drones in weddings , Grand , Indian Bride entry with russians arounds , Wide variety of Indian Wedding Tasty food , malai chaap to gulab jamun , jalebi rabri , ice cream , Kids wearing skivi sweater under lehenga to deal with winter weddings , the struggles of Rishta before Marraige , Dealing with dowry , Every Girls struugles , Indian mom and super excited for daughter wedding , dreaming about grandchidlren , her beti being a maa one day , buying and placing a lot indian snacks daal kachori , samosa , pakore , dry fruits & nuts , barati ready for baraat dance on dhol , tired from 7 days of shadi functions , haldi , cocktail , sangeet , god tikka , mehendi , god bharai , halwai at home , indian relatives and theri demands , exclusive parlour makeup , hd bridal makeup , celebrity makeup , airbrush makeup , glitter makeup , high wedding makeup and hairstyle prices , wonder ladies with babies in wedding and doing rasams , dealing traffic jam while reaching a shaadi , every girls efforts of getting in lehenga , jhumka , doing makeup and then getting out of lehenga , removing heavy layers of makeup before sleeping , removing jwelery bangles , high heels , going on honeymoon and celebrating New Year goa , newyork , paris , london , switerland , enjoying bhaji , mathi achar , bondi ladoo , with tea or masala Chai , Going to Chandi Chowk for bridal shopping , choosing from wide variety of Bride lehenga color choices , red , maroon , pink , blue , green , trying different designs sabyasachi , manish malhotra , celebrity bridal lehengas , lehenga from jaipur with heavy embroidery work , crazy lehenga shopkeppers , high prices of lehenga and bargaining in that , bride not able to diet near marraige eating outside food golgappe to curb with full day of wedding shopping , after wedding counting money got from shagun , decorating gold daimond jewelry in front of indian guest buidling new homes before marraige , saas bahu happy in their new mother daughter relationship , kids mesmerized by new snippet.title: How To Train Your Dragon | Official Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
How To Train Your Dragon - In Theaters June 13

From three-time Oscar¬Æ nominee and Golden Globe winner Dean DeBlois, the creative visionary behind DreamWorks Animation‚Äôs acclaimed How to Train Your Dragon trilogy, comes a stunning live-action reimagining of the film that launched the beloved franchise. 
On the rugged isle of Berk, where Vikings and dragons have been bitter enemies for generations, Hiccup (Mason Thames; The Black Phone, For All Mankind) stands apart. The inventive yet overlooked son of Chief Stoick the Vast (Gerard Butler, reprising his voice role from the animated franchise), Hiccup defies centuries of tradition when he befriends Toothless, a feared Night Fury dragon. Their unlikely bond reveals the true nature of dragons, challenging the very foundations of Viking society. 

With the fierce and ambitious Astrid (BAFTA nominee Nico Parker; Dumbo, The Last of Us) and the village‚Äôs quirky blacksmith Gobber (Nick Frost; Snow White and the Huntsman, Shaun of the Dead) by his side, Hiccup confronts a world torn by fear and misunderstanding. 
As an ancient threat emerges, endangering both Vikings and dragons, Hiccup‚Äôs friendship with Toothless becomes the key to forging a new future. Together, they must navigate the delicate path toward peace, soaring beyond the boundaries of their worlds and redefining what it means to be a hero and a leader. 

The film also stars Julian Dennison (Deadpool 2), Gabriel Howell (Bodies), Bronwyn James (Wicked), Harry Trevaldwyn (Smothered), Ruth Codd (The Midnight Club), BAFTA nominee Peter Serafinowicz (Guardians of the Galaxy) and Murray McArthur (Game of Thrones).
How to Train Your Dragon is written, produced and directed by DeBlois. It is also produced by three-time Oscar¬Æ nominee Marc Platt (Wicked, La La Land) and Emmy winner Adam Siegel (Drive, 2 Guns). How To Train Your Dragon is part of the Filmed For IMAX¬Æ Program, which offers filmmakers IMAX¬Æ technology to help them deliver the most immersive movie experience to audiences around the world. 

Inspired by Cressida Cowell‚Äôs New York Times bestselling book series, DreamWorks Animation‚Äôs How to Train Your Dragon franchise has captivated global audiences, earning four Academy Award¬Æ nominations and grossing more than $1.6 billion at the global box-office. Now, through cutting-edge visual effects, DeBlois transforms his beloved animated saga into a breathtaking live-action spectacle, bringing the epic adventures of Hiccup and Toothless to life with jaw-dropping realism as they discover the true meaning of friendship, courage and destiny.

Sunn Mere Dil Episode 14 [Eng Sub] Digitally Presented by LUX - Happilac Paints and Ujooba Beauty Cream - Wahaj Ali - Maya Ali - 21st November 2024 - Har Pal Geo

Sunn Mera Dil Digitally Presented by LUX - Happilac Paints and Ujooba Beauty Cream

7th Sky Entertainment‚Äôs highly anticipated mega signature project, Sunn Mere Dil, is the most awaited drama serial. The mega drama boasts a star-studded cast led by Wahaj Ali and Maya Ali. Written by the renowned Khalil Ur Rehman Qamar and directed by the acclaimed Haseeb Hasan, Sunn Mere Dil promises to be a one-of-a-kind drama.

Sunn Mere Dil is a tale in which love finds a new meaning, where one person‚Äôs devotion quietly flourishes, often unnoticed. Their heart beats for someone who may never truly understand the depth of their feelings. Yet, in their silent sacrifices, they realize that true love is not about
possession but about selflessness.

Every unspoken gesture and unseen act of kindness brings them fulfillment, as they put their beloved‚Äôs happiness above their own, showing that love is not just about being together, it‚Äôs about redefining happiness, even at the expense of their contentment.

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Director: Haseeb Hasan
Writer: Khalil Ur Rehman Qamar
